  "Code examples, JSON Schemas, and machine-readable policy templates are licensed under the MIT License unless otherwise stated. You may deploy them on your own sites freely.": "Ihe atụ koodu, JSON Schema, na ntụle amụma igwe ọrụ ga-agụ nwere ikike ọrụ n'okpuru MIT License ma ọ bụrụ na akọwaghị ya n'ụzọ ọzọ. Ị nwere ike itinye ha na weebụ nke gị n'efu efu.",
