  "Convert rights declarations into a workable licensing market instead of a binary open/closed web.": "Gbanwee nkwupụta ikike ka ọ bụrụ ahịa ikike ọrụ enwere ike ịrụ ọrụ na ya kama weebụ eeh/mba emeghere/emechiri.",
  "Copied ✓": "E depụtala ✓",
