  "Correct positioning: independent research drafts, protocol proposals, and an open specification experiment.": "Ọnọdụ ziri ezi: ndepụta nchọpụta nweere onwe ya, atụmatụ protocol, na nnwale nkọwa emeghere emeghe.",
  "Corrected an earlier default: Belgium (BE) now maps to Dutch instead of French — Flemish speakers are the country’s majority (~60%) over Walloon French speakers (~40%).": "Edoziri ihe ndabere e kesịrị mbụ: Belgium (BE) ugbu a na-eso Dutch kama French — ndị na-asụ Flemish bụ ọnụ ọgụgụ kachasị n'obodo ahụ (ihe dịka 60%) karịa ndị na-asụ Walloon French (ihe dịka 40%).",
  "Corrected an earlier default: Kazakhstan (KZ) now maps to Kazakh instead of Russian, now that a Kazakh translation exists — the same kind of fix as the earlier Belgium correction.": "Edoziri ihe ndabere e kesịrị mbụ: Kazakhstan (KZ) ugbu a na-eso Kazakh kama Russian, ebe ntụgharị asụsụ Kazakh dịzị adị ugbu a — otu ụdị mmezi ahụ e mere na Belgium na mbụ.",
